quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  38,43,"Min nje…ói mo …ďeynguure makko nden, e yeru ma…ď…ďe tawti …ďe, yurmeende immorde e amen, e waaju wonan'de mar…ďe haqqille …ďen."
  38,44,""Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere hu…óo, piyiraa …óum [cuddii…óo maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)". Min tawu mo, mu√Ī√Īii…óo. O mo∆ī∆īii jiyaa…óo. Pellet, ko o …óuu…óu…óo tuubugol-ruttoo."
  38,45,"JaŇčto kadi, jiyaa…ďe Amen …ďen, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraa…ďe semmbe e yi'an…óe."
  38,46,"Min keertinanii …ďe heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) …óen."
  38,47,"E kadi …ďee ka amen, ko jiyaa…ďe e su…ďaa…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe su…ďaa…ďe."
  38,48,"JaŇčto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala ma…ď…ďe, ko jiyaa…ďe e su…ďaa…ďe."
  38,49,"∆äum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, ruttorde mo∆ī∆īunde."
  38,50,"∆äuum ko Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, …ói …ďe udditanaa dame mum,"
  38,51,"hara ko …ďe so…ď…ďindii …ďe ton, he…ďe nodda ton muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói e njaram."
  38,52,"Hino woodani …ďe (ton): ra…ď…ďu…ďe ndaar…óe, goree…ďe."
  38,53,"Ko …óum woni ko poda…óon, fii √Ďalaande hasboore ndeen."
  38,54,"Pellet, …óum ko arsike amen, gasugol alanaa mo."
  38,55,"∆äuum, [ko njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe]. Pellet, hino woodani kadi bew…ďe …ďeen, ko …ďuri bonnde e ruttorde,"
  38,56,"woni Jahannama, nge …ďe naatoyta. Nge bonii nda…ó…óudi!"
  38,57,"∆äuum, ko yo …ďe mee…ó: ko fatata, e ∆īi∆ī∆īiri,"
  38,58,"Wo…ď…ďe …ďen, nanndu…óe e majje, ko nooneeji."
  38,59,"E hino dental naatiroyat ngal doole e mon, toolii alanaa …ďe; tawde ko …ďe naatoo…ďe Yiite !"
  38,60,"∆Āeen mbia: bismilla alanaa mon, ko onon ndefi min …óum". Nge bonii √Īii…ďirde."
  38,61,"∆Āe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, defu…óo min …óuim on, …ďeydan mo leptte cowalle ka Yiite"."